Author: becruxrubbish
Title: [ANN][ICO] ARQUTE Global Animation Studio
Body: A total of 10,000,000 (ten million) AGAS tokens will be issued. Of these, for sale will be 9 million (Nine million) + 200,000 (Two hundred thousand) bonus for wholesale buyers. At the closed presale will be realized 1 000 000 (One million) AGAS tokens. In the course of the Pre-ICO, up to 2,000,000 (Two million) AGAS tokens will be sold. During the ICO, up to 4,000,000 (Five million) AGAS tokens + unsold tokens with Pre-ICO will be sold. During Pro-ICO, up to 2,000,000 (Two million) AGAS tokens + unallocated tokens from the previous stage will be sold. The remaining 800,000 (Eight hundred thousand) AGAS tokens will be distributed between the ICO team and partners. Thus, 92% of the total number of tokens are sold.

Body: Thanks for your feedback. Of course, we do not compare with Hollywood projects, where tens of millions of dollars are immediately invested in advertising.  Join us on the pre-ico, while the price of the token is minimal. Author: ARQUTE G.A.S
Title: [ANN][ICO] ARQUTE Global Animation Studio
Body: Thanks for the feedback. The studio is created as a co-entity, which will be managed by a common vote. We assemble projects into our case, for further work on them together with all participants. Since a large focus group guarantees a quality product. In our portfolio there are released products that you can evaluate: Fixies, Masha and the Bear and others.  Unfortunately or fortunately, we are just good animators and we are not professionals in ico. We made sinple bounty, but we do not understand their differences.  Join us on the pre-ico, while the price of the token is minimal. Next, it will double to ico and again to pro-ico.
